<section id="contactme" class="px-4 py-16 bg-secondary">
  <h2
    class="uppercase font-bold text-3xl md:text-5xl tracking-widest text-center"
  >
    Contacto
  </h2>
  <div class="bg-primary w-[48px] h-[5px] rounded-full mx-auto mt-5"></div>
  <p
    class="text-center mt-5 text-text-color md:text-lg lg:text-2xl max-w-screen-lg mx-auto"
  >
    Si deseas contactarme, puedes llenar el siguiente formulario o escribirme a
    mi correo electrónico y me pondré en contacto contigo lo más pronto posible.
  </p>
  <form
    action=""
    class="bg-white p-6 lg:p-12 rounded-md mt-8 max-w-screen-lg mx-auto"
  >
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-4">
      <div>
        <label
          for="name"
          class="text-text-color font-bold md:text-lg lg:text-xl tracking-wider"
          >Nombre</label
        >
        <input
          type="text"
          id="name"
          name="name"
          placeholder="Ingrese su nombre"
          class="w-full p-3 lg:p-4 mt-2 bg-text-color/30 rounded-sm placeholder:text-text-color/40 placeholder:font-bold text-text-color focus:outline-none text-lg lg:text-xl"
        />
      </div>
      <div>
        <label
          for="email"
          class="text-text-color font-bold md:text-lg lg:text-xl tracking-wider"
          >Correo Electrónico</label
        >
        <input
          type="email"
          id="email"
          name="email"
          placeholder="Ingrese su correo electrónico"
          class="w-full p-3 lg:p-4 mt-2 bg-text-color/30 rounded-sm placeholder:text-text-color/40 placeholder:font-bold text-text-color focus:outline-none text-lg lg:text-xl"
        />
      </div>
      <div>
        <label
          for="message"
          class="text-text-color font-bold md:text-lg lg:text-xl tracking-wider"
          >Mensaje</label
        >
        <textarea
          name="message"
          id="message"
          cols="30"
          rows="10"
          placeholder="Escriba su mensaje"
          class="w-full p-3 lg:p-4 mt-2 bg-text-color/30 rounded-sm placeholder:text-text-color/40 placeholder:font-bold text-text-color focus:outline-none text-lg lg:text-xl"
        ></textarea>
      </div>
      <button
        type="submit"
        class="w-full lg:w-max uppercase bg-primary text-white font-bold py-2 lg:py-3 px-10 lg:px-16 rounded-md mt-4 block mx-auto lg:mx-0 md:text-lg lg:text-xl lg:justify-self-end"
      >
        Enviar
      </button>
    </div>
  </form>
</section>
